## 為什麼革命性
傳統流程：
1. 後端寫 API
2. 寫 OpenAPI 或 Swagger
3. 前端 codegen 生成 client
4. 前端用 client 呼叫

tRPC 流程：
1. 後端寫 API（自動有 TS 型別）
2. 前端直接 import 後端的型別、呼叫

## 後端：定義 router
```typescript
// server/router.ts
import { initTRPC } from "@trpc/server";
import { z } from "zod";

const t = initTRPC.create();

export const appRouter = t.router({
  user: t.router({
    list: t.procedure
      .query(async () => {
        return await db.users.findMany();
      }),

    byId: t.procedure
      .input(z.string())
      .query(async ({ input }) => {
        return await db.users.findUnique({ where: { id: input } });
      }),

    create: t.procedure
      .input(z.object({
        name: z.string(),
        email: z.string().email(),
      }))
      .mutation(async ({ input }) => {
        return await db.users.create({ data: input });
      }),
  }),
});

export type AppRouter = typeof appRouter;
```

## 前端：直接呼叫
```typescript
// client.ts
import { createTRPCProxyClient, httpBatchLink } from "@trpc/client";
import type { AppRouter } from "../server/router";

const trpc = createTRPCProxyClient<AppRouter>({
  links: [httpBatchLink({ url: "/api/trpc" })],
});

// 型別 100% 安全
const users = await trpc.user.list.query();
const u = await trpc.user.byId.query("abc-123");
const newUser = await trpc.user.create.mutate({
  name: "Alice",
  email: "a@x.com"
});
```

## React 整合
```typescript
import { useQuery, useMutation } from "@tanstack/react-query";

function UserList() {
  const { data: users } = trpc.user.list.useQuery();
  const create = trpc.user.create.useMutation();

  return (
    <>
