## RFC 6902 JSON Patch
```json
[
  { "op": "replace", "path": "/name", "value": "Alice" },
  { "op": "add", "path": "/tags/-", "value": "vip" },
  { "op": "remove", "path": "/age" },
  { "op": "copy", "from": "/old", "path": "/new" },
  { "op": "move", "from": "/a", "path": "/b" },
  { "op": "test", "path": "/version", "value": 5 }
]
```

## 6 種 op
- **add**：加新欄位
- **remove**：刪欄位
- **replace**：改欄位
- **copy**：複製
- **move**：搬移
- **test**：測試值（不對則整個 patch 失敗）

## 套用 Patch
```javascript
import { applyPatch } from "fast-json-patch";

const original = { name: "Alice", age: 25 };
const patch = [
  { op: "replace", path: "/name", value: "Bob" },
  { op: "remove", path: "/age" },
];

const result = applyPatch(original, patch).newDocument;
// { name: "Bob" }
```

## 產生 Diff
```javascript
import { compare } from "fast-json-patch";

const before = { name: "Alice", age: 25 };
const after = { name: "Bob", email: "b@x.com" };

const diff = compare(before, after);
// [
//   { op: "replace", path: "/name", value: "Bob" },
//   { op: "remove", path: "/age" },
//   { op: "add", path: "/email", value: "b@x.com" }
// ]
```

## REST API 使用
```http
PATCH /users/123 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json-patch+json

[
  { "op": "replace", "path": "/email", "value": "new@x.com" }
]
```

## JSON Merge Patch（RFC 7396、更簡單）
```json
{ "email": "new@x.com", "age": null }
```
- 直接寫新值
- `null` 代表刪除
- 不能改陣列特定 index

```http
PATCH /users/123
Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json

{ "email": "new@x.com" }
```

## 用途
- **協作編輯**：每個 user 的改動傳 patch
- **DB audit log**：記錄每次改了什麼
- **離線同步**：累積 patch、上線後送
- **API 增量更新**：節省頻寬

## 真實案例
- **Figma**：multiplayer 用類似機制
- **Notion**：協作編輯
- **CRDT 工具**：Y.js / Automerge

